(0, 0, 0); line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tEscape<br />\n\tEscape means to get away from. What or who is escaping? Where does the escape happen? What will be the outcome?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They escaped... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) escape from jail<br />\n\t2) escape velocity needed<br />\n\t3) plan of escape<br />\n\t4) an escape route<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tThe designer was thoughtful as he looked at the people going by him. Under all the glamorous lighting and upbeat music, the club was a good place for escape. As to what was really going on at the establishment behind the scene, the designer was sure that not that people were aware nor would they care to find out. They just wanted a place to let their mind escape, to get away from their everyday routine, even for a brief moment. The designer pondered, and was lost in this thoughts as he continued his way back.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/1710018211389/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p869703/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p869703\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p987843/\">2017全年英语考试时间表</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p981281/\">考完四六级，你离英语大牛还有多远？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p989426/\">2016年12月大学英语六级作文解析及范文</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2