  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://img1.cache.netease.com/catchpic/2/20/2013C1F311EB57B1DB6729CB32F93314.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p992111\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tBut first to Yemen, with the world's attention focused on how to tackle Islamic State in Syria and Iraq, the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/conflict\" target=\"_blank\">conflict</a> in Yemen has largely been forgotten. There has been daily <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/bombing\" target=\"_blank\">bombings</a> since March this year by a Saudi-led <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/coalition\" target=\"_blank\">coalition</a> trying to get rid of the rebel Houthis who are a Shia group. Now the Saudi-led coalition says a seven-day <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/ceasefire\" target=\"_blank\">ceasefire</a> with Shia Houthi rebels has come into force, the truce coincides with the start of UN-sponsored peace talks in Switzerland. Imogen Foulkes reports from Geneva where the talks are taking place.</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;The UN has told both <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/negotiating\" target=\"_blank\">negotiating</a> sides that making peace requires courage. The agenda for the talks is <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/ambitious\" target=\"_blank\">ambitious</a>: a permanent ceasefire to follow the temporary one, the withdrawal of armed groups and heavy weapons, better access for aid agencies and prisoner exchanges. These measures cannot be agreed in a day or two. UN diplomats say the talks will 'take the necessary time'.&quot;</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a>英语</a><span>&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。&gt;&gt;<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/course/52569?source=16553\